name: The ultimate lock unlocker
description:
What do you think, who is the better?  Human or PC?

In this test you will have to try and unlock a lock. If you can beat the PC in time or accuracy then glory to humans we win, but if the PC wins then we are srewed. AIs going to rule the world. Any ways you just have to tip a number. It's not that hard. Who can't tip a number? No one, so just do it. If you are wondering why did I do this: It is just an experiment. Good luck!
